               burglariously and feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17900224-56-victim547" type="victimName">
                           Philip 
                           Goads
                        <interp inst="t17900224-56-victim547" type="surname" value="Goads"></interp>
